     Pride also discusses the U.S. economy and labor market. PEAK6 Investments LP's Jud Pyle also speaks. They speak with Carol Massar, Matt Miller, Adam Johnson and Dominic Chu on Bloomberg Television's "Street Smart." (Source: Bloomberg)  
                           

     
